ComfoConnect Home Assistant Custom Component
Copyright 2025 Tim van der Hoorn

This product includes software developed by the Home Assistant Core Team
and Michiel Arnauts.

This component is based on the official Home Assistant ComfoConnect integration:
https://github.com/home-assistant/core/tree/dev/homeassistant/components/comfoconnect

Original Authors:
- Michiel Arnauts (https://github.com/michaelarnauts)
- Home Assistant Core Team

The original integration and this custom component both use the pycomfoconnect library:
https://github.com/michaelarnauts/comfoconnect

This custom component adds the following enhancements:
- Device registry support for proper device grouping in Home Assistant
- Config flow for UI-based configuration
- Automatic setup of all available sensors

